  "bodyText": "To apply for a marriage license or for questions regarding marriage requirements contact the Ministry of Home Affairs.\n\n## Directory\n\nMinistry of Home Affairs and Information <br/> Jones Building <br/> Webster Business Park <br/> Wildey, St. Michael <br/>\n\n| Role | Telephone |\n| --- | --- |\n| PBX | (246) 535-7260 |\n| Minister | (246) 535-0434 |\n| Permanent Secretary | (246) 535-7261 |\n| PS Secretary | (246) 535-7273 |\n| Deputy Permanent Secretary | (246) 535-7262 |\n| Financial Comptroller | (246) 535-7268 |\n| Senior Admin Officer | (246) 535-7263 |\n| Executive Officer | (246) 535-7270 |\n| FAX | (246) 535-7286 |"
}
